<section id="about" class="about">
  <header>
    <h2>About</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="about__content">
      <div class="bg-pattern-ring"></div>
      <picture>
        <source
          media="(min-width: 800px)"
          srcset="/images/avatar-desktop.webp"
          width="100%"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/avatar-mobile.webp"
          alt="A man sitting behind a sunset, relaxed, with an amazing smile."
          width="450px"
        />
      </picture>

      <div class="about__text">
        <p>Hello again!</p>
        <p>
          I’m Johnny Estrada, a web developer with 3 years of hands-on
          experience in <span class="green">React</span>, <span class="green"
            >TypeScript</span
          >, <span class="green">Tailwind</span>, <span class="green"
            >Express</span
          >, <span class="green">Node.js</span>, and <span class="green"
            >MySQL</span
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          Exciting news—I’ve just launched a <a href="https://www.klarity.online">tracking web app</a>
          that’s live and ready for action!
        </p>
        <p>
          I’m also developing a Shopify e-commerce site and working on an
          interpreter in Go. Stay tuned for their release!
        </p>

        <p>
          Outside of coding, I’m into 3D printing and its endless possibilities.
          When I’m not at the computer, you’ll probably catch me paddleboarding
          in the bay.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

